summary.span: 一代表架构库中架构的整个集合的对象。

span.span: A collection of objects that represents the entire collection of schemas in the Schema Library.

span.para: Microsoft Word 中，您可以从模板和加载项对话框中的 XML 架构选项卡访问架构库。架构库代表用户已应用到 Word 文档或用户使用架构库对话框中显式添加到架构库的用户的计算机上安装的架构。
使用要返回的单个XMLNameSpace对象的XMLNamespaces集合的属性。Item属性的索引值可以是一个整数，它指示架构的架构库中的位置或字符串，代表架构的名称，使用返回属性 (TargetNamespace 设置架构中定义）。

In Microsoft Word, you can access the Schema Library from the XML Schema tab in the Templates and Add-ins dialog box. The Schema Library represents schemas installed on a user's machine that a user has applied to a Word document or that a user has explicitly added to the Schema Library by using the Schema Library dialog box.

Use the property of the XMLNamespaces collection to return an individual XMLNameSpace object. The index value of the Item property can be either an Integer, which indicates the position of the schema in the Schema Library, or a String, which represents the name of the schema as returned by using the property (the TargetNamespace setting defined in the schema).

summary.span: 返回一个 32 位整数，它指示在其中创建指定的对象的应用程序。

span.span: Returns a 32-bit integer that indicates the application in which the specified object was created.

remarks.span:
如果 Microsoft Word 中创建对象，此属性返回十六进制数字 4d535744，表示字符串"MSWD。"此值也可以由常量wdCreatorCode。主要设计
Creator属性用于 Macintosh，其中每个应用程序具有四个字符的创建者代码。例如，Microsoft Word 具有 MSWD 的创建者代码。有关此属性的其他信息，请咨询的语言参考 Microsoft Office Macintosh Edition 中包含的帮助。

span.para: If the object was created in Microsoft Word, this property returns the hexadecimal number 4D535744, which represents the string "MSWD." This value can also be represented by the constant wdCreatorCode.

The Creator property was primarily designed to be used on the Macintosh, where each application has a four-character creator code. For example, Microsoft Word has the creator code MSWD. For additional information about this property, consult the language reference Help included with Microsoft Office Macintosh Edition.
